originalText.text: Dr. Wachtel is easily the best psychiatrist I have ever had the pleasure of partnering with; and it truly is a partnership. She is thorough in her analysis and deeply understands the medicine she is discussing. She is well-versed in her field and understands the importance of balancing medicine and therapy. I have never felt more understood and heard than when meeting and speaking with Dr. Wachtel; because of her attentiveness and knowledge, I feel confident in the medicine I am taking and the progress we have made together. I was seeking a psychiatrist with compassion and understanding, but also someone I felt I could be honest and open with, no matter what. I am beyond grateful for her wisdom and guidance. If you have additional questions about my experience, I would be happy to be of support.

originalText.text: Dr. Wachtel has been a great doctor for me. She understood my needs right away and tailored a great treatment for me to deal with stress. She explains the medication needed. I have been with Dr. Wachtel for a couple of months now, but already seeing significant improvement in my daily life. I strongly recommend her.

originalText.text: I’ve been seeing Dr. Wachtel for over 2 years now and has been very helpful for me. She makes sure she gets an overall picture of her patient’s mental and physical health  to provide the right treatment. She’s caring and easy to talk to, which creates a comfortable environment for each session.

originalText.text: Dr. Wachtel is a treasure. What I've valued the most over seeing her for the past four months is the way she shares her rationale and opinions about my treatments, and how I can be an active participant in my own mental health with her. She is compassionate and candid, and I feel so proud of the progress that she and I have made together. Her background in internal medicine has also been helpful in sorting out the relationships between different medical and mental health conditions.
